flowchart TD
    Start([Visitor arrives]) --> HasAcct{Has an account?}

    HasAcct -- No --> Reg[Open Register]
    Reg --> RegForm[Enter name, email, password]
    RegForm --> RegValid{Valid & email unique?}
    RegValid -- No --> RegErr[Show validation error] --> RegForm
    RegValid -- Yes --> CreateUser[Create customer account<br/>hash password]
    CreateUser --> Welcome[Send welcome notification] --> LoggedIn

    HasAcct -- Yes --> Login[Open Login]
    Login --> Creds[Enter email & password]
    Creds --> AuthChk{Credentials valid?}
    AuthChk -- No --> LoginErr[Show generic error] --> Creds
    AuthChk -- Yes --> StatusChk{Account status?}
    StatusChk -- Suspended --> Blocked[Block + show suspended message] --> Login
    StatusChk -- Active --> IssueToken[Issue Sanctum token] --> LoggedIn

    LoggedIn([Authenticated session]) --> Account[Account area]
    Account --> A1[Update profile info]
    Account --> A2[Change password]
    Account --> A3[Logout - revoke token]
    A1 --> Saved[Save & confirm]
    A2 --> PwChk{Current password ok?}
    PwChk -- No --> PwErr[Error] --> A2
    PwChk -- Yes --> Saved
    A3 --> End([Session ended])
